      <title>镰状细胞基因疗法进展缓慢</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/sections/shots-health-news/2024/09/19/nx-s1-4978692/sickle-cell-gene-therapies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[距离美国食品药品管理局批准第一种镰状细胞病基因疗法已经过去了近一年。到目前为止，只有少数患者接受了这种期待已久的治疗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/sections/shots-health-news/2024/09/19/nx-s1-4978692/sickle-cell-gene-therapies</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
